{"tid":1042111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講到高質嘅廣東話翻唱主題曲一定要提轟轟戰隊","createTime":"2019-03-01T10:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T11:56:38.000Z","uid":209097,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2b62912a5aa61f05b9b488a4af6aef13592074","tid":1042111,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E2HsKPI27Es\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE2HsKPI27Es&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=5c191b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E2HsKPI27Es</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主係音痴唔係好聽得出啱唔啱音，所以音準方面先唔講。單係歌詞就應該屌打哂大部分廣東話主題曲。<br />\n<br />\n成首歌詞都係同探險，文物有關，配合番轟轟戰隊嘅主題。<br />\n<br />\n當中有句:誰心中都有獨特瑰寶。依句呼應左入面紅戰士嘅口頭禪:每個人心中都有屬於自己嘅寶物。<br />\n<br />\n然後嗰句:狂龍在舞 邪力駕到 強敵殺到。指嘅係入面嘅反派。狂龍-龍王 邪力-高賈 <del>強敵-暗之刃</del> <br />\n<br />\n之後有句：心魔陰險想法自私 徬徨裡激生勇士。講緊去到後面黑戰士因為自己內心黑暗俾反派利用，最後自我突破並且ko番反派轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n最精彩係句:能源用了 亦不止 轟響心底的鬥志。劇透緊大結局嗰陣原本啲裝備嘅能量俾boss吸哂用唔到，但最後係靠心入面嘅鬥志同冒險精神當做能源驅動。<br />\n<br />\n一首歌詞可以講哂成套劇嘅主題，並且暗示埋入面發生嘅事，埋下彩蛋。莫講話翻唱嘅歌，就算係原裝日文主題曲都未必做到，所以講到高質嘅翻唱一定要提轟轟戰隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def7d34495845e89bf2d6ef8234c44f7999349c5","tid":1042111,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"想屌啲戰士😹"},{"pid":"4813226b926a81cb7c611704a684a638118d8313","tid":1042111,"uid":34443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"填詞人功力深厚"},{"pid":"cd384e5a56fe0fd0642eb2460382122fd60e5dab","tid":1042111,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sb9-b39u3l4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsb9-b39u3l4&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=e6be7be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sb9-b39u3l4</a>"},{"pid":"f7bd7574e03d9972897d6ff331fe2d6b818be987","tid":1042111,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4813226b926a81cb7c611704a684a638118d8313","tid":1042111,"uid":34443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"填詞人功力深厚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"唔好話我老屎忽，以前啲填詞人高而家嗰啲幾班，單係用心嘅程度就已經拋離哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1fb0ebc1875eaa7addbad97e73b4979271967","tid":1042111,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd384e5a56fe0fd0642eb2460382122fd60e5dab","tid":1042111,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sb9-b39u3l4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsb9-b39u3l4&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=e6be7be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sb9-b39u3l4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"龍騎個首都好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f53dc0b878ddbe1c4682d34e167884d628cc38","tid":1042111,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"即係個詞人睇曬先填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdcb37bd3de4e3b5cc34a0c6f853b08d34a268a","tid":1042111,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f53dc0b878ddbe1c4682d34e167884d628cc38","tid":1042111,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"即係個詞人睇曬先填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"正常就會睇幾集，不過依位睇黎就唔止幾集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f9bd7ccbaf2cb2a1bb75c96d4f4e3a1475d0ac","tid":1042111,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"狄易達又唱得幾好聽"}]}